                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18421128-227-offence-1 t18421128-cd-208"></join>18th of Nov</rs>.;1 pestle, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; and 1 mortar, 15<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18421128-name-1176" type="victimName">
